skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my passion
des: Say, "Alexa, open My Passion" and you'll hear what others are passionate about. Maybe it will inspire you. What's your passion? This is a compilation of ALL of our passions. Contact me by email, twitter, Facebook, or a YouTube comment on one of my videos, and let me know what your passion is. I'll add it here, and I'll put your name on it. If you happen to share the same passion with others, I'll add your name.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
